        <h1>WELCOME TO JOKE GENERATOR™!!!!</h1>
        <h2 id="header2-1"> Do too many people like you/enjoy your presence? JOKE GENERATOR™ can change that! </h2>
        <h2 id="header2-2"> Customize you joke here! </h2>
